I came across these exact images in documents back in late 2005 on a web 
site that Google had cached on their server with no blacked out areas.  In 
those days, Google was caching intranets that where accessible from the 
open web.  It was over 20 pages of information on these devices, along with 
name of people, whom I can not recall working on the reverse engineering of 
these devices. On one of the pages it details how they discovered that the 
writing glyph on the devices controlled its function/purpose.  It also went 
into great detail that the black semi circle half parts where solid with no 
computer technology as we use today.  At the time I was on a restricted 
network with no way to make hard copies or save to computer media. It's a 
shame nobody else has come across these documents and provided them to the 
public. Also included was what appeared to be some sort of star map with 
many of the same unusual writing and pictures.  From what I was reading, 
and the many peoples name listed in the documents along with their 
findings, these objects appeared to be authentic. That's all I can recall. ﻿
